0references%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it's%20part%20of%20what%20drives%20the%20intense%20fandom%20that%20drives%20her%20success%20and%20made%20her%20a%20billionaire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPuth%20is%20one%20of%20the%20more%20baffling%20references%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20namedrop%20began%20to%20spread%20before%20the%20album's%20official%20release%20since%20it%20leaked%20early%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20viral%20social-media%20questions%20whether%20the%20leak%20was%20real%2C%20suggesting%20the%20Puth%20reference%20made%20so%20little%20sense%20that%20it%20could%20point%20to%20the%20leak%20being%20an%20AI-generated%20fake.%20But%20it%20was%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20possible%20connection%20could%20be%20Puth's%20love%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Puth%20confirmed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Ffeatures%2Fcharlie-puth-voicenotes-interview-billboard-cover-story-2018-8097384%2F%3Fref%3Dpopsugar.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBillboard%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20had%20a%20fling%20with%20Selena%20Gomez%3A%20%26quot%3BVery%20short-lived%2C%20very%20small%2C%20but%20very%20impactful.%20And%20it%20really%20messed%20me%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20romance%20inspired%20a%20song%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20Don't%20Talk%20Anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20two%20sang%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20of%20his%20songs%2C%20%26quot%3BAttention%2C%26quot%3B%20seems%20to%20line%20up%20with%20his%20romance%20with%20Gomez%20(although%20he%20hasn't%20confirmed%20that%20it's%20about%20her).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20song%20prompted%20some%20backlash%20after%20he%20explained%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP7Hp5SYHNuY%26ab_channel%3DGenius%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20video%20for%20the%20lyrics%20website%20Genius%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20was%20about%20a%20former%20girlfriend%20turning%20down%20his%20sexual%20advances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20be%20talk