20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fnagaland%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENagaland%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Friday%20afternoon%2C%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fenpo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEastern%20Nagaland%20People's%20Organisation%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20which%20is%20demanding%20a%20separate%20administration%20with%20more%20financial%20autonomy%20-%20declared%20a%20'public%20emergency'%20and%20called%20on%20locals%20to%20boycott%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20north-eastern%20state's%20Chief%20Election%20Officer%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20ENPO%20for%20disrupting%20the%20electoral%20process.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20top%20poll%20official%20said%20the%20group%20had%20attempted%20%26quot%3Bto%20use%20undue%20influence...%20by%20interfering%20with%20the%20free%20exercise%20of%20those%20residing%20in%20Eastern%20Nagaland%20areas%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20general%20election%26quot%3B.%20The%20ENPO%2C%20the%20officer%20said%2C%20is%20therefore%20%26quot%3Bdirected%20to%20show%20cause...%20as%20to%20why%20action%20under%20subsection%20of%20Section%20171C%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20should%20not%20be%20initiated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relevant%20subsection%20says%20%26quot%3Bwhoever%20voluntarily%20interferes%2C%20or%20attempts%20to%20interfere%2C%20with%20the%20free%20exercise%20of%20any%20electoral%20right%20commits%20the%20offence%20of%20undue%20influence%20at%20the%20election%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnagaland-group-decides-to-boycott-lok-sabha-polls-over-separate-state-5337373%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENagaland%20Group%20Decides%20To%20Boycott%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ENPO%20has%20responded%20saying%20the%20%26quot%3Bmain%20goal%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20public%20notification%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Breduce%20the%20possibility%20of%20disturbances%20in%20the%20Eastern%20Nagaland%20region%2C%20which%20is%20under%20our%20jurisdiction%2C%20and%20the%20risk%20linked%20with%20gatherings%20of%20anti-social%20elements%26quot%3B.%20The%20organisation%20underlined%20the%20fact%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Eastern%20Nagaland%20region%20is%20presently%20under%20Public%20Emergency%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20that%20this%20was%20declared%20after%20consultations%20with%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bvoluntary%20initiative%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20people%2C%20the%20ENPO%20said%2C%20arguing%20that%20action%20under%20Section%20171C%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20applicable...%20as%20no%20offence%20related%20to%20undue%20influence%20at%20any%20election%20is%20committed...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20that%20the%20shutdown%20was%20a%20voluntary%20initiative%20by%20the%20people%2C%20there%20was%20no%20question%20of%20coercion%20or%20enforcement%20by%20the%20ENPO%20or%20any%20other%20authority%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said%2C%20also%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20willing%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20%26quot%3Bif%20there%20has%20been%20any%20misunderstanding%20or%20misinterpretation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2030%20the%20ENPO%20held%20a%20lengthy%20closed-door%20meeting%20with%2020%20MLAs%20and%20other%20organisations%2C%20at%20which%20they%20reiterated%20the%20decision%20to%20totally%20abstain%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20Eastern%20Nagaland%20Legislators'%20Union%20-%20consisting%20of%20the%2020%20MLAs%20-%20had%20asked%20the%20ENPO%20to%20reconsider%20its%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Live%20Coverage%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-phase-1-live-updates-voting-to-begin-at-7-am-5471946%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELok%20Sabha%20Elections%20Phase%201%202024%20Live%20Updates%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%