protein%20helped%20her%20lose%20140%20pounds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20she%20didn't%20cut%20out%20treats%20but%20found%20some%20healthier%20swaps%20and%20focused%20on%20high-protein%20meals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20right%20balance%20of%20nutrients%20can%20make%20weight%20loss%20easier%20by%20helping%20you%20feel%20full%20for%20longer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20necessarily%20have%20to%20resign%20yourself%20to%20cutting%20carbs%20or%20skipping%20dessert%20to%20lose%20weight.%20A%2038-year-old%20mom%20of%20two%20said%20she%20lost%20140%20pounds%20in%20two%20years%20without%20restricting%20her%20favorite%20foods%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feating-more-protein-help-women-healthy-aging-positive-impact-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeating%20more%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20tracking%20her%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20summer%202022%2C%20Andrea%20Pence%20decided%20it%20was%20time%20to%20make%20a%20change.%20The%20Tennessee%20resident%20realized%20her%20routine%20had%20left%20her%20feeling%20constantly%20tired%2C%20dealing%20with%20achy%20joints%2C%20and%20struggling%20to%20stay%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20tired%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20didn't%20realize%20just%20how%20fatigued%20I%20was%2C%20just%20how%20rundown%20I%20was.%20I%20had%20pain%20in%20my%20knees%20and%20pain%20in%20my%20back%2C%20I%20was%20getting%20out%20of%20breath%20just%20walking%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20coordinated%20by%20the%20health%20app%20MyFitnessPal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPence%20said%20her%20initial%20goal%20was%20to%20lose%20about%2090%20pounds.%20She%20lost%20a%20total%20of%20140%20pounds%2C%20got%20rid%20of%20sleep%20apnea%2C%20and%20boosted%20her%20energy%20enough%20to%20exercise%20daily%2C%20Pence%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20learning%20to%20be%20more%20aware%20of%20calorie%20counts%20(no%20surprise%2C%20she%20uses%20MyFitnessPal)%20was%20a%20big%20help%2C%20but%20the%20game%20changer%20was%20getting%20more%20protein%20in%20her%20diet.%20That%20shift%20helped%20her%20to%20feel%20fuller%20for%20longer%2C%20so%20she%20could%20still%20eat%20her%20favorite%20foods%2C%20just%20in%20moderation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20before%20and%20after%20pictures%20showing%20140%20pound%20weight%20loss%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66196e6f3f923f7dab076d31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrea%20Pence%20said%20she%20lost%20more%20than%20100%20pounds%20by%20eating%20more%20protein%20and%20tracking%20calories.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andrea%20Pence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEating%20more%20protein%20can%20help%20you%20feel%20full%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPence%20said%20tracking%20meals%20helped%20her%20to%20see%20that%20she%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnot-eating-enough-protein-fat-loss-goals-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20getting%20enough%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20underestimated%20how%20important%20the%20nutrient%20is%20for%20managing%20appetite%20on%20a%20weight%20loss%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20given%20up%20in%20the%20past%20when%20I've%20tried%20because%20it's%20been%20so%20frustrating.%20You%20don't%20see%20results%20and%20then%20you're%20hungry%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BProtein%20was%20absolutely%20100%25%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20things.%20If%20you%20go%20heavy%20on%20protein%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20full.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20she%20aims%20for%20around%20100%20grams%20of%20protein%20daily%20(within%20the%20range%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-protein-maximize-muscle-gains-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20much%20protein%20dietitians%20recommend%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20about%200.7%20grams%20per%20pound%20of%20body%20weight%20daily).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPence%20said%20she%20typically%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F30-10-rule-simple-diet-hack-eat-more-protein-dietitian-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-protein%20breakfast%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Greek%20yogurt.%20She%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprocessed-foods-with-protein-fiber-better-for-you-expert-says-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esubstitutes%20higher-protein%20versions%20of%20convenience%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20bagels%20and%20microwave%20meals%20for%20lunch%20and%20dinner.%20However%2C%20Pence%20said%20it's%20worth%20having%20some%20ice%20cream%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20make%20it%20healthy%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20desserts%20and%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20there's%20not%20a%20lower%20calorie%20swap%2C%20and%20that's%20OK%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20don't%20have%20to%20cut%20out%20foods%20you%20love%20to%20lose%20weight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPence%20said%20she%20didn't%20cut%20out%20any%20food%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20helped%20me%20do%20this%20for%20the%20long%20haul%20is%20I've%20not%20cut%20anything%20out%20that%20I've%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20true%3A%20Dietitians%20have%20previously%20told%20BI%20it's%20not%20necessary%20to%20follow%20a%20specific%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-lose-weight-by-eating-more-according-to-dietitians-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweight-loss%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20low-carb%2C%20intermittent%20fasting%2C%20or%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiet%20culture%20has%20people%20out%20here%20thinking%20you%20have%20to%20eat%20this%20bland%20salad%20with%20grilled%20chicken%20every%20day%2C%20and%20that%20is%20all%20you%20can%20eat%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPence%20said%20she%20had%20previously%20tried%20losing%20weight%20by%20eating%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%26quot%3B%20foods%2C%20like%20fruit%20and%20granola%20parfaits%2C%20but%20she%20later%20realized%20they%20had%20more%20calories%20than%20she%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20mindful%20of%20total%20calories%20and%20finding%20ways%20to%20fit%20in%20more%20protein%20helped%20Pence%20enjoy%20her%20food%20while%20still%20meeting%20her%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20want%20a%20cheeseburger%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20have%20a%20cheeseburger%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-lost-140-pounds-by-eating-more-protein-tracking-meals-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713523562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6619896b3f923f7dab0780c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-lost-140-pounds-by-eating-more-protein-tracking-meals-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2038-year-old%20mom%20of%20two%20said%20she%20surpassed%20her%20weight%20loss%20goal%20after%20eating%20more%20high-protein%20foods%20like%20Greek%20yogurt%20to%20help%20her%20feel%20full.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22glandsverk%40insider.com%20(Gabby%20Landsverk)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-lost-140-pounds-by-eating-more-protein-tracking-meals-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wipro%20Q4%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20drops%208%25%20to%20Rs%202%2C835%20cr%2C%20revenue%20down%204.2%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713523460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-01%2F15%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1705314077-8862.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%2