ved%20donations%20through%20bonds.%20Is%20that%20extortion%20as%20well%3F%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20must%20tell%20the%20people%2C%20yes%2C%20we%20have%20also%20extorted.%20And%20the%20donation%20they%20have%20received%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20number%20of%20MPs%20is%20more%20than%20what%20we%20got.%20They%20don't%20have%20an%20issue%2C%20there%20is%20no%20allegation%20of%20corruption%20against%20us.%20So%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20confusion.%20They%20won't%20be%20successful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20verdict%20on%20February%2015%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20scrapped%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20violates%20the%20citizens'%20right%20to%20information.%20The%20scheme%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20was%20unconstitutional%20and%20arbitrary%20and%20may%20lead%20to%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangement%20between%20political%20parties%20and%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20bench%20of%20five%20judges%20held%20that%20the%20stated%20objective%20of%20fighting%20black%20money%20and%20maintaining%20the%20confidentiality%20of%20donors%20cannot%20defend%20the%20scheme.%20Electoral%20bonds%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20are%20not%20the%20only%20way%20to%20curb%20black%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20in%20data%20released%20by%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20made%20public%20by%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20found%20to%20have%20received%20maximum%20funds%20through%20these%20bonds%20--%20Rs%206%2C986.5%20crore%20--%20since%20they%20were%20introduced%20in%202018.%20The%20BJP%20was%20followed%20by%20Trinamool%20Congress%20at%20Rs%201%2C397%20crore%20and%20Congress%20at%20Rs%201%2C334%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713523380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F1j87nid8_amit-shah-rahul-gandhi-split_625x300_19_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findi