0replacing%20individual%20desks%20with%20more%20round%20tables%20that%20fit%20several%20people%2C%20while%20creating%20extra%20lounge%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20philosophy%20was%20echoed%20by%20Patricia%20Pomies%2C%20the%20company's%20global%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWas%20remote%20work%20really%20a%20mistake%3F%20Do%20we%20need%20a%20fixed%20amount%20of%20days%20to%20go%20to%20the%20office%3F%20I%20would%20not%20go%20as%20far%20as%20saying%20people%20lack%20inspiration%20when%20working%20from%20home.%20At%20Globant%2C%20we%20firmly%20believe%20in%20autonomy%20and%20in%20giving%20flexibility%20to%20every%20team%20to%20decide%20how%20they%20work%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said%20on%20X%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWas%20remote%20work%20really%20a%20mistake%3F%20Do%20we%20need%20a%20fixed%20amount%20of%20days%20to%20go%20to%20the%20office%3F%20I%20would%20not%20go%20as%20far%20as%20saying%20people%20lack%20inspiration%20when%20working%20from%20home.%20At%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobant%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Globant%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20firmly%20believe%20in%20autonomy%20and%20in%20giving%20flexibility%20to%20every%20team%20to%20decide%20how%20they%20work%20best.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FVj5sQYzmC7%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FVj5sQYzmC7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Patricia%20Pomies%20(%40PatPomies)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPatPomies%2Fstatus%2F1763673611305390197%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20times%2C%20people%20from%20the%20same%20POD%20are%20not%20even%20in%20the%20same%20country.%20As%20a%20tech%20company%2C%20having%20a%20digital%20office%20and%20remote%20working%20is%20simply%20baseline%20common%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20culture%20of%20her%20company%20is%20such%20that%20employees%20find%20it%20%26quot%3Bvaluable%26quot%3B%20to%20meet%20in-person%2C%20not%20because%20they%20are%20told%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGloban't%20decision%20is%20in%20contrast%20with%20the%20approach%20of%20Apple%2C%20Alphabet%20Inc's%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%20Corp%20and%20Meta%2C%20which%20have%20all%20adopted%20policies%20to%20bring%20employees%20back%20to%20their%20desks.%20In%20India%20too%2C%20the%20issue%20has%20generated%20a%20lot%20of%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20Zerodha%20CEO%20Nithin%20Kamath%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20remote%20office%20concept%20did%20not%20work%20for%20some%20of%20his%20employees%20and%20proved%20challenging%20for%20those%20in%20tech%2C%20business%2C%20and%20decision-making%20positions%20due%20to%20communication%20barriers.%20He%20also%20noted%20that%20ever%20since%20some%20of%20his%20staff%20started%20returning%20to%20office%20on%20a%20hybrid%20basis%2C%20the%20results%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bdramatically%20positive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20IBM%20had%20delivered%20a%20companywide%20ultimatum%20to%20managers%20who%20are%20still%20working%20remotely%3A%20move%20near%20an%20office%20or%20leave%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713523020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fv71d4cl_work-from-home_625x300_01_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftech-company-globant-allows-all-30-000-employees-to-work-from-home-5477115%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Globan't%20decision%20is%20in%20contrast%20with%20the%20approach%20of%20Apple%2C%20Alphabet%20Inc's%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%20Corp%20and%20Meta%2C%20which%20have%20all%20adopted%20policies%20to%20bring%20employees%20back%20to%20their%20desks.%20In%20India%20too%2C%20the%20issue%20has%20generated%20a%20lot%20of%2