's%20popularity%20has%20grown%20so%20that%20we%20can%20get%20votes%20and%20seats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20increased%20vote%20share%20between%20the%202014%20and%202019%20as%20another%20sign%20that%20the%20BJP's%20reach%20in%20South%20India%2C%20a%20region%20that%20has%20traditionally%20rejected%20the%20party%2C%20should%20now%20result%20in%20seat%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202014%20election%20the%20BJP%20polled%205.5%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20This%20fell%20to%20less%20than%203.7%20in%202019.%20In%20neighbouring%20Kerala%2C%20the%20party%20got%20a%20little%20over%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes%20in%202014%20and%20that%20increased%20to%2012.93%20per%20cent%20five%20years%20later.%20However%2C%20the%20party%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20seat%20in%20either%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20historically%20struggled%20most%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Kerala.%20The%20party%20has%2C%20however%2C%20poured%20significant%20resources%2C%20including%20Mr%20Modi's%20time%2C%20into%20campaigning%20in%20these%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20has%20made%20over%20a%20dozen%20visits%20between%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Kerala%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comment%20comes%20as%20all%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu's%2039%20seats%20vote%20today%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala's%2020%20seats%20vote%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20on%20April%2026%2C%20while%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%2025%20do%20so%20in%20the%20fourth%20phase%20on%20May%2013.%20Telangana%2C%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20made%20dramatic%20gains%20in%20last%20year's%20Assembly%20poll%2C%20going%20from%20one%20seat%20in%202018%20to%20eight%20this%20time%2C%20has%2017%20constituencies%20that%20also%20vote%20May%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-news-karnataka-bjp-jds-alliance-bjp-vs-bjp-c