20comments%20on%20specific%20military%20actions%20linked%20to%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlights%20were%20suspended%20in%20Isfahan%20and%20the%20Iranian%20cities%20of%20Tehran%20and%20Shiraz%20as%20well%20as%20airports%20across%20the%20country's%20western%20borders%2C%20but%20those%20restrictions%20were%20soon%20eased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20follows%20days%20of%20frantic%20diplomacy%20from%20the%20US%20and%20European%20nations%20in%20which%20they%20tried%20to%20convince%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20not%20to%20respond%20too%20aggressively%2C%20if%20at%20all%2C%20to%20Saturday%20night's%20Iranian%20attack.%20Their%20main%20concern%20is%20to%20avoid%20a%20wider%20war%20in%20a%20region%20already%20roiled%20by%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20and%20which%20could%20send%20oil%20prices%20above%20%24100%20a%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrude%20and%20gold%20initially%20jumped%20in%20early%20trading%20on%20Friday%2C%20but%20later%20pared%20their%20gains%20as%20reports%20suggested%20the%20apparent%20attack%20was%20far%20from%20extensive.%20A%20senior%20Iranian%20military%20official%20also%20said%20Tehran%20had%20already%20responded%20to%20Israeli%20threats%2C%20and%20didn't%20blame%20the%20Jewish%20state%20for%20the%20latest%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsfahan%20is%20home%20to%20around%202%20million%20people%20and%20several%20military%20bases%20and%20facilities.%20It's%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20one%20of%20several%20launch%20sites%20for%20Iran's%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20Saturday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20said%20two%20Israeli%20officials%20confirmed%20their%20nation%20was%20behind%20the%20strike.%20The%20newspaper%20also%20reported%20a%20military%20air%20base%20near%20Isfahan%20was%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20notified%20the%20US%20on%20Thursday%20it%20planned%20to%20retaliate%20in%20the%20next%2024-48%20hours%2C%20two%20American%20officials%20said%20to%20Bloomberg.%20They%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20discussing%20private%20conversations.%20Spokespeople%20for%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20and%20the%20Pentagon%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrent%20crude%20oil%20climbed%20above%20%2490%20a%20barrel%20before%20trading%20around%20%2487.80%20as%20of%209%20a.m.%20in%20London%2C%20up%20less%20than%201%25%20on%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGold%20also%20quickly%20reversed%20its%20jump.%20Yields%20on%2010-year%20US%20Treasuries%20%E2%80%94%20another%20haven%20for%20global%20investors%20in%20times%20of%20geopolitical%20stress%20%E2%80%94%20fell%20around%20four%20basis%20points%20to%204.59%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shekel%20weakened%20this%20week%20to%20its%20lowest%20level%20in%202024%2C%20though%20was%20steady%20on%20Friday%20at%203.78%20per%20dollar.%20That%20was%20despite%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Ratings%20downgrading%20Israel%20by%20one%20level%20to%20A%2B%20%E2%80%94%20still%20easily%20in%20investment-grade%20territory%20%E2%80%94%20hours%20before%20the%20reported%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20had%20vowed%20to%20retaliate%20against%20Iran%20for%20its%20barrage%20of%20more%20than%20300%20drones%20and%20missiles%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20which%20were%20destroyed%20before%20hitting%20their%20targets.%20While%20there%20was%20limited%20damage%20and%20no%20one%20was%20killed%2C%20Israel%20said%20it%20would%20send%20a%20message%20of%20weakness%20to%20Iran%20and%20its%20other%20enemies%20if%20it%20didn't%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20said%20it%20was%20a%20justified%20reaction%20to%20a%20strike%20on%20its%20embassy%20compound%20in%20Syria%20on%20April%201%2C%20which%20killed%20several%20Iranian%20officers%20and%20was%20blamed%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20Europe%20and%20Arab%20states%20urged%20Netanyahu%20to%20act%20with%20restraint.%20The%20foreign%20ministers%20of%20the%20UK%20and%20Germany%20both%20traveled%20to%20Israel%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20see%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20faced%20a%20dilemma%20this%20week.%20While%20many%20of%20his%20far-right%20coalition%20members%20insisted%20on%20a%20firm%20response%2C%20the%20Israeli%20public%20was%20split%20on%20whether%20the%20country%20should%20react%20at%20all.%20Many%2C%20according%20to%20a%20poll%2C%20said%20it%20wasn't%20worth%20provoking%20Iran%20and%20straining%20Israel's%20ties%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20more%20than%20six%20months%20into%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20and%20still%20intent%20on%20attacking%20the%20city%20of%20Rafah%2C%20where%20it%20says%20several%20thousand%20Hamas%20fighters%20are%20lodged.%20Many%20in%20the%20country%20want%20the%20government%20to%20focus%20on%20finishing%20the%20conflict%20against%20the%20Iran-backed%20militant%20group%20that%20launched%20a%20deadly%20invasion%20on%20Oct.%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBall%20in%20Iran's%20Court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20attributed%20to%20Israel%2C%20the%20nature%20and%20scope%20of%20the%20strike%20on%20Friday%20%E2%80%94%20including%20any%20casualties%20%E2%80%94%20could%20determine%20whether%20the%20tit-for-tat%20responses%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20escalate%20or%20start%20to%20get%20scaled%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ball%20is%20in%20Iran's%20court%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ziad%20Daoud%2C%20chief%20emerging-market%20economist%20for%20Bloomberg%20Economics.%20%26quot%3BThe%20most%20likely%20scenario%20is%20avoiding%20escalation%20through%20another%20direct%20attack%20on%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20analysts%20had%20said%20targeting%20Iran's%20nuclear%20facilities%20would%20be%20the%20riskiest%20and%20most%20aggressive%20option%20open%20to%20Israel%2C%20with%20strikes%20on%20non-nuclear%20military%20facilities%20and%20cyberattacks%20among%20the%20less%20escalatory%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20indications%20are%20that%20this%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsymbolic%20attack%26quot%3B%20that%20won't%20force%20Iran%20to%20respond%20aggressively%2C%20retired%20Israeli%20General%20Israel%20Ziv%20told%20the%20nation's%20Channel%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20hawkish%20national%20security%20minister%2C%20Itamar%20Ben%20Gvir%2C%20suggested%20he%20wasn't%20happy%20with%20his%20country's%20apparent%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWeak%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20one-word%20post%20on%20X%20in%20Hebrew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBen%20Gvir%20isn't%20part%20of%20Netanyahu's%20Likud%20party%20and%20doesn't%20sit%20in%20the%20five-man%20war%20cabinet%20that%20takes%20final%20decisions%20on%20military%20actions.%20But%20he's%20key%20to%20the%20survival%20of%20Netanyahu's%20coalition%20and%20said%20after%20Iran's%20attack%20that%20Israel%20had%20to%20hit%20back%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIranian%20media%20portrayed%20a%20sense%20of%20calm%20in%20Isfahan%20and%20asserted%20that%20everything%20was%20proceeding%20as%20normal.%20The%20country's%20Supreme%20National%20Security%20Council%20decided%20against%20convening%20for%20an%20emergency%20meeting%2C%20according%20to%20state%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20was%20bracing%20for%20a%20reprisal%20by%20Israel%20all%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETehran%20has%20routinely%20accused%20Israel%20of%20attacks%20and%20sabotage%20activities%20targeting%20its%20nuclear%20and%20military%20sites%20in%20the%20past%2C%20including%20in%20Isfahan%2C%20home%20to%20some%20key%20nuclear%20enrichment%20and%20missile%20facilities.%20Iran%20says%20its%20nuclear%20program%20is%20for%20peaceful%20purposes%20but%20the%20West%20accuses%20it%20of%20seeking%20to%20develop%20atomic%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Iran%20said%20it%20may%20reconsider%20its%20nuclear%20policies%20if%20Israel%20attacked%20its%20atomic%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIranian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Hossein%20Amirabdollahian%20also%20warned%20Israel%20against%20lashing%20out%20after%20the%20weekend%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20case%20the%20Israeli%20regime%20embarks%20on%20adventurism%20again%20and%20takes%20action%20against%20the%20interests%20of%20Iran%2C%20the%20next%20response%20from%20us%20will%20be%20immediate%20and%20at%20a%20maximum%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20to%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713518520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fn5lg3m0g_iran-attacks-israel-reuters-_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-israel-iran-hostilities-flare-up-ball-in-tehrans-court-now-5476533%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20launched%20a%20retaliatory%20strike%20on%20Iran%20following%20last%20week's%20missile%20and%20drone%20barrage%20from%20Tehran%2C%20according%20to%20two%20US%20officials%2C%20though%20media%20from%20both%20countries%20appeared%20to%20downplay%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-israel-iran-hostilities-flare-up-ball-in-tehrans-court-now-5476533%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-israel-iran-hostilities-flare-up-ball-in-tehrans-court-now-5476533%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-israel-iran-hostilities-flare-up-ball-in-tehrans-court-now-5476533%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20LSD%202%20-%20Stumper%20Of%20A%20Film%20Embraces%20Its%20Campy%2C%20Pulpy%20Spirit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20dichotomy%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flove-sex-aur-dhoka-2-trailer-into-the-deep-dark-digital-world-5427690%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ELove%20Sex%20Aur%20Dhokha%202%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20makes%20itself%20instantly%20apparent.%20The%20film%20probes%20the%20not-so-secret%20virtual%20lives%20of%20a%20generation%20of%20youngsters%20with%20severely%20limited%20attention%20spans%20even%20as%20it%20demands%20complete%20focus%20on%20its%20bewilderingly%20whimsical%20flow%20of%20images%20and%20sounds.%20You%20take%20your%20eyes%20off%20the%20screen%20or%20let%20your%20mind%20wander%20for%20a%20split%20second%20and%20you%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20missing%20a%20crucial%20piece%20of%20information%20or%20a%20prickly%20flash%20of%20an%20image%20that%20is%20meant%20to%20speaks%20volumes.%20With%20its%20constant%20zaniness%20and%20unpredictability%2C%20the%20film's%20rhythm%20reflects%20the%20untamable%20impatience%20of%20technology-obsessed%2C%20instant%20fame-seeking%20influencers%20and%20YouTubers%20who%20inhabit%20a%20world%20of%20their%20own%20for%20better%20or%20for%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flove-sex-aur-dhoka-2-trailer-into-the-deep-dark-digital-world-5427690%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reveals%20the%20many%20ways%20in%20which%20violence%2C%20physical%20and%20psychological%2C%20is%20perpetrated%20on%20those%20who%20exist%20within%20the%20heady%20bubble%20and%20also%20on%20those%20who%20live%20outside%20it.%20This%20outright%20stumper%20of%20a%20film%20embraces%20its%20campy%2C%20pulpy%20spirit%20with%20all%20its%20might%20as%20it%20satirizes%20society%20that%20is%20led%20by%20technology%20in%20directions%20that%20it%20cannot%20fully%20grasp%2C%20not%20as%20yet%20at%20nay%20rate.%20By%20the%20time%20%3Cem%3ELSD%203%3C%2Fem%3E%20happens%2C%20we%20will%20probably%20know%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flove-sex-aur-dhoka-2-trailer-into-the-deep-dark-digital-world-5427690%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20raises%20questions%2C%20some%20playful%2C%20others%20pointed%2C%20even%20profound%2C%20about%20a%20world%20in%20which%20fake%2C%20nearly%20always%2C%20trumps%20fact.%20There%20is%20a%20heavy%20price%20to%20be%20paid%20for%20the%20surrender%20to%20the%20lure%20of%20constantly%20evolving%20technology%2C%20as%20the%20three%20principal%20characters%20in%20the%20film%20discover%20mostly%20at%20their%20own%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWritten%20by%20director%20and%20co-producer%20Dibakar%20Banerjee%20with%20Prateek%20Vats%20and%20Shubham%20(the%20writers%20of%20Eeb%20Allay%20Ooo!)%2C%20the%20Ekta%20Kapoor-produced%20%3Cem%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20repeats%20the%20three-part%20interlinked%20structure%20of%20%3Cem%3ELSD%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20made%20nearly%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20ago%20and%20addressed%20the%20impact%20of%20recording%20devices%20that%20impinged%20on%20people's%20privacy%20and%20endangered%20their%20lives%20and%20mental%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2014%20years%20that%20have%20elapsed%20between%20the%20two%20films%2C%20both%20the%20hardware%20and%20the%20software%20have%20evolved%20to%20a%20point%20where%20the%20line%20between%20the%20real%20and%20the%20virtual%2C%20and%20the%20tangible%20and%20the%20deepfake%2C%20can%20be%20erased%20at%20the%20push%20of%20a%20button.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20appears%20to%20thrive%20on%20leading%20double%20lives%20but%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20vanishing%20margins%20between%20the%20imagined%20and%20the%20factual%2C%20many%20are%20increasingly%20falling%20prey%20to%20manipulation%20and%20the%20danger%20of%20self-harm.%20That%20is%20the%20principal%20thematic%20burden%20of%20%3Cem%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20although%20it%20isn't%20in%20the%20least%20interested%20in%20telling%20the%20audience%20what%20to%20make%20of%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20people%20it%20is%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExploring%20gender%20fluidity%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20isn't%20remotely%20self-conscious%2C%20%3Cem%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20replaces%20the%20subheads%20of%20Love%2C%20Sex%20and%20Dhokha%20with%20Like%2C%20Share%20and%20Download.%20Each%20segment%20portrays%20the%20struggles%20of%20individuals%20trying%20to%20leap%20out%20of%20the%20boxes%20that%20a%20myopic%20society%20shoves%20them%20into%2C%20then%20slams%20the%20lid%20shut%20and%20keeps%20strict%20vigil%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20segment%2C%20a%20transwoman%2C%20Noor%20(Paritosh%20Tiwari)%2C%20who%20aspires%20to%20be%20an%20acclaimed%20actress%2C%20is%20a%20participant%20in%20a%20garish%20reality%20show%20-%20it%20is%20called%20Truth%20Ya%20Naach.%20It%20requires%20her%20to%20put%20her%20life%20under%20the%20public%20spotlight.%20Noor%20goes%20on%20and%20off%20camera%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20higher%20ratings%20as%20her%20rivals%20snap%20at%20her%20heels%20and%20keep%20her%20on%20her%20toes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20producers%20of%20the%20show%20-%20in%20the%20judges'%20seats%20are%20Sophie%20Chaudhry%2C%20Tusshar%20Kapoor%20and%20Anu%20Malik%20(the%20only%20one%20of%20the%20three%20who%20does%20not%20play%20himself)%20-%20manipulate%20her%20into%20a%20reunion%20with%20her%20estranged%20mother%20(Swaroopa%20Ghosh).%20The%20mother's%20first%20reaction%20on%20seeing%20Noor%20after%20a%20two-year%20hiatus%20is%20%26quot%3Bdublaa%20ho%20gaya%20hai%26quot%3B.%20She%20is%20still%20averse%20to%20accepting%20her%20altered%20sexual%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnu%20Malik's%20character%20throws%20a%20fit%20when%20the%20mother%20croons%20and%20the%20daughter%20dances%20to%20the%20song.%20Ordering%20the%20duo%20to%20stop%2C%20he%20thunders%3A%20%26quot%3BMaa%20se%20badhkar%20kuch%20nahin%20hain%26quot%3B.%20He%20follows%20that%20up%20with%20a%20mushy%20ode%20to%20motherhood.%20It%20is%20apparent%20that%20his%20outburst%20is%20scripted.%20The%20ratings%20go%20through%20the%20roof%20and%20it%20is%20revealed%20that%20this%20bit%20of%20the%20show%20has%20been%20sponsored%20%26quot%3BMaa%20Ki%20Mamta%20Aata%20(Mother's%20Love%20Flour).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20ratings%20and%20the%20truth%20meter%20-%20a%20method%20to%20measure%20the%20veracity%20of%20statements%20that%20the%20participants%20make%20on%20the%20show%20-%20yo-yo-ing%20wildly%2C%20Noor%20is%20under%20constant%20pressure%20to%20'perform'%20her%20transition%20for%20the%20consumption%20of%20the%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20process%20of%20gender%20assertion%20is%20reduced%20to%20a%20game%20controlled%20by%20the%20producers%20of%20the%20show%2C%20the%20sponsors%2C%20the%20public%20at%20large%20and%2C%20last%20but%20not%20the%20least%2C%20the%20anti-vulgarity%20clause%20in%20the%20rules%20that%20govern%20broadcasting.%20Technology%20and%20a%20society%20that%20is%20in%20voyeuristic%20mode%2024%2F7%2C%20personal%20desire%20has%20been%20snatched%20away%20by%20the%20collective%20will%20of%20those%20whose%20''likes%26quot%3B%20can%20make%20or%20break%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20part%20of%20%3Cem%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20too%2C%20has%20a%20third-gender%20character%2C%20Kulu%20(Bonita%20Rajpurohit)%2C%20struggling%20with%20the%20consequences%20of%20being%20who%20she%20is.%20She%20is%20strapped%20for%20cash%20and%20unapologetic%20about%20using%20her%20body%20to%20earn%20her%20a%20few%20rupees%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKulu%20works%20on%20the%20cleaning%20team%20at%20a%20Metro%20Rail%20station%20in%20Delhi.%20Her%20boss%2C%20Lovina%20Singh%20(Swastika%20Mukherjee)%2C%20single%20mother%20of%20a%20school-going%20boy%20(who%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20the%20link%20between%20this%20story%20and%20the%20next)%2C%20feigns%20sympathy%20for%20her%20employee%20when%20she%20gets%20into%20serious%20trouble%20and%20is%20in%20danger%20of%20losing%20her%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20mounting%20pressure%20from%20the%20head%20honcho%2C%20Lovina%20does%20her%20best%20to%20control%20the%20damage%20that%20the%20negative%20publicity%20for%20her%20company%20-%20which%20seeks%20mileage%20out%20of%20giving%20employment%20to%20transgenders%20-%20but%20with%20every%20move%20that%20she%20makes%20she%20only%20succeeds%20in%20exposing%20her%20own%20and%20her%20firm's%20double%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20only%20in%20the%20virtual%20world%20that%20things%20are%20phony.%20In%20fact%2C%20if%20things%20are%20fake%20in%20the%20images%20and%20claims%20that%20float%20around%20in%20a%20hyper-connected%20universe%2C%20they%20are%20only%20a%20reflection%20of%20all%20the%20pretence%20that%20is%20constantly%20sought%20to%20be%20passed%20off%20as%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20exactly%20what%2018-year-old%20school%20boy%20Shubham%20Narang%20(Abhinav%20Singh)%2C%20Game%20Paapi%20in%20the%20virtual%20world%2C%20does%20in%20his%20avatar%20as%20a%20hyper-masculine%20dude.%20Artificial%20intelligence%2C%20virtual%20reality%20and%20metaverses%20have%20flip%20sides%20that%20extract%20a%20high%20price%20from%20those%20who%20play%20along%20and%20lose%20themselves%20in%20the%20dead-end%20algorithm-driven%20labyrinths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20great%20thing%20about%20a%20Dibakar%20Banerjee%20film%20is%20that%20it%20never%20fails%20to%20spring%20surprises.%20LSD%202%20has%20more%20than%20its%20share%20of%20fearless%20flights%20of%20fancy.%20Some%20land%2C%20some%20don't.%20But%20that%20takes%20little%20away.%20Even%20when%20it%20tends%20to%20be%20baffling%2C%20the%20film%20makes%20you%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20cinema%20that%20excites%20you%2C%20%3Cem%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20might%20be%20well%20worth%20your%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713518340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F75568sto_lsd2_625x300_19_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flove-sex-aur-dhokha-2-review-outright-stumper-of-a-film-embraces-its-campy-pulpy-spirit-3-stars-5476524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Love%20Sex%20Aur%20Dhokha%202%20Review%3A%20The%20great%20thing%20about%20a%20Dibakar%20Banerjee%20film%20is%20that%20it%20never%20fails%20to%20spring%20surprises.%20LSD%202%20has%20more%20than%20its%20share%20of%20fearless%20flights%20of%20fancy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flove-sex-a