ent%20against%20Naxalism.%20It%20is%20not%20democratic%20and%20should%20be%20eradicated.%20I%2C%20PM%20Modi%20and%20everyone%20have%20appealed%20to%20welcome%20those%20who%20lay%20down%20their%20weapons.%20But%20if%20you%20pick%20up%20arms%2C%20you%20will%20get%20an%20answer%20from%20security%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20told%20NDTV%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETuesday's%20clash%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Hapatola%20forest%20near%20Binagunda%20village%20within%20Chhattisgarh's%20Kanker%20district.%20A%20joint%20operation%20conducted%20by%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20and%20the%20state%20police's%20District%20Reserve%20Guard%20(DRG)%20led%20to%20a%20fierce%20gun%20battle.%20Three%20security%20personnel%20sustained%20injuries%20-%20two%20from%20the%20BSF%20and%20one%20from%20the%20DRG%2C%20underlining%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20called%20this%20encounter%20fake.%20When%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20there%20were%20no%20operations%20against%20Naxals.%20In%2090%20days%2C%20our%20government%20launched%20an%20operation%2C%2087%20Naxals%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20123%20Naxals%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20253%20have%20surrendered%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Chief%20Minister%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai's%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%20December%202023%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20witnessed%20a%20surge%20in%20proactive%20counterinsurgency%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pace%20with%20which%20things%20are%20being%20done%2C%20Naxalism%20will%20be%20completely%20eradicated%20from%20India%20in%20one%20or%20two%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20home%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETuesday's%20operation%20in%20Kanker%20adds%20to%20the%20tally%20of%2079%20Maoists%20felled%20in%20separate%20engagements%20with%20security%20forces%20this%20year%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Bastar%20region%2C%20which%20encompasses%20seven%20dist