content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20Warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20bullying%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClose%20your%20eyes%20and%20remember%20a%20situation%20where%20you%20wished%20you%20had%20said%20%E2%80%98no%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20theatre%20teacher%20to%20a%20class%20full%20of%20students%2C%20including%20Sandhya%20Nair.%20The%20next%20prompt%20was%20to%20ask%20everyone%20in%20the%20class%20to%20say%20%E2%80%98no%E2%80%99.%20Sandhya%20found%20it%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20utter%20this%20powerful%20two-letter%20word.%20She%20tried%20and%20tried%2C%20but%20found%20herself%20unable%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20was%20this%20simple%20act%20so%20challenging%20for%20the%20then-teenager%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20Kamathipura%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Sandhya%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20a%20sex%20worker.%20She%20recalls%20being%20bullied%20and%20shamed%20in%20school%20when%20other%20children%20found%20out%20about%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284501%2Fmumbai-bangladesh-sex-trade-worker-mothers-day-love-rescue%2F%5C%22%3Emother%E2%80%99s%20profession%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Growing%20up%2C%20she%20was%20repeatedly%20told%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20daughter%20of%20a%20sex%20worker%20will%20become%20a%20sex%20worker%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20taught%20to%20hate%20my%20mother%20and%20my%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sandhya%20in%20a%20free-flowing%20interaction%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmilaap.org%2Ffundraisers%2Fhelp-survivors-of-trafficking-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmilaap.org%2Ffundraisers%2Fhelp-survivors-of-trafficking-1%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20class%2C%20she%20recalls%20breaking%20down%20and%20crying%20out%20a%20resounding%20%E2%80%9Cno%E2%80%9D%20that%20shook%20everyone%20present%20there.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20she%20spoke%20out%20about%20being%20raped%2C%20confiding%20in%20her%20mentor%2C%20Robin%20Chaurasiya.%20Sandhya%20recalls%20this%20moment%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20path-breaking%20ones%20in%20her%20life%20at%20the%20time%2C%20when%20she%20was%2018%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20happened%20thanks%20to%20the%20theatre%20class%20and%20therapy%20sessions%20conducted%20by%20%E2%80%98Kranti%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20NGO%20that%20empowers%20children%20of%20sex%20workers%20to%20become%20agents%20of%20social%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti1-1713281048.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kranti%20provides%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20daughters%20of%20sex%20workers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti1-1713281048.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti1-1713281048-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti1-1713281048-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti1-1713281048-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti1-1713281048-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347423%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKranti%20provides%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20daughters%20of%20sex%20workers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%20started%20its%20work%20at%20Kamathipura%2C%20known%20as%20the%20red%20light%20area%20in%202011%20for%20daughters%20of%20sex%20workers%20and%20survivors%20of%20trafficking.%20Children%20here%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20access%20to%20a%20good%20education%20and%20opportunities%20to%20build%20a%20better%20life.%20Kranti%20removes%20this%20stigma%20associated%20with%20being%20the%20child%20of%20a%20sex%20worker%20and%20empowers%20these%20young%20girls%20to%20achieve%20their%20full%20potential%2C%20unburdening%20them%20from%20years%20of%20societal%20conditioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20Sandhya%E2%80%99s%20example.%20From%20being%20a%20child%20who%20hated%20going%20to%20school%2C%20she%20is%20today%20pursuing%20an%20MA%20in%20gender%20and%20peacebuilding%20at%20the%20University%20for%20Peace%20in%20Costa%20Rica.%20Sandhya%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20girls%20from%20Kranti%20who%20are%20pursuing%20their%20postgraduate%20studies%20in%20foreign%20universities%2C%20and%20working%20on%20bringing%20about%20social%20change%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20girls%20like%20them%20in%20brothels%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20was%20bullied%20for%20my%20dark-coloured%20skin%20and%20mother%E2%80%99s%20profession%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%E2%80%99s%20mother%20had%20big%20dreams%20for%20her%20daughter.%20She%20wanted%20Sandhya%20to%20be%20educated%20in%20a%20private%20school%20and%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20trying%20to%20get%20her%20admitted%20into%20one.%20But%20there%20was%20a%20problem%3A%20if%20she%20disclosed%20her%20profession%2C%20no%20school%20would%20admit%20Sandhya%2C%20so%20her%20mother%20chose%20to%20instead%20say%20that%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20domestic%20help.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273849%2Fhero-smarajit-jana-durbar-collective-helps-kolkata-sex-worker-get-rights%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggles%20of%20the%20young%20girl%20%3C%2Fa%3Estarted%