20was%20a%20local%20pastor%20who%20convinced%20her%20to%20let%20him%20train%20again%20with%20the%20belief%20that%20it%20would%20amount%20to%20something%20better.%20In%202016%2C%20Chungreng%20came%20back%20to%20wrestling.%20To%20help%20chase%20his%20dream%2C%20his%20mother%20worked%20even%20harder%2C%20sold%20whatever%20she%20could%20grow%2C%20and%20found%20work%20in%20Imphal.%20The%20four%20of%20them%20(Chungreng%2C%20his%20mother%2C%20wife%20and%20child)%20moved%20to%20a%20one-room%20residence%20near%20the%20Khuman%20Lampak%20area.%20While%20he%20was%20training%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20construction%20labourer%20in%20the%20afternoon%20and%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chungreng%20Koren%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347403%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChungreng%20Koren%20worked%20in%20construction%20to%20support%20his%20dreams%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20training%20for%20nearly%20two%20years%2C%20he%20qualified%20for%20the%20National%20Games%20competing%20in%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%2072%20kg%20category.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20sponsor%20my%20travel%20and%20training%2C%20my%20mother%20went%20back%20to%20our%20village%20and%20collected%20money%20by%20asking%20everyone%20to%20contribute%20whatever%20amount%20they%20could%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20National%20Games%20were%20slated%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Goa%20in%20November%202017%2C%20Chungreng%20decided%20to%20train%20at%20the%20SAI%20facility%20in%20Rohtak%2C%20Haryana.%20For%20a%20month%20before%20the%20event%2C%20he%20trained%20well%20but%20the%20event%20was%20postponed%20with%20no%20date%20in%20sight%20of%20when%20it%20was%20going%20to%20happen.%20It%20was%20a%20devastating%20blow.%20The%20next%20National%20Games%20would%20only%20take%20place%20in%20Gujarat%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manipur%20MMA%20legend%20Chungreng%20Koren%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347395%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChungreng%20Koren%20overcame%20so%20much%20in%20life%20to%20become%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20standout%20MMA%20fighters%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMMA%20calling%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20wrestling%20career%20not%20going%20anywhere%2C%20Chungreng%20decided%20to%20call%20Roshan%20Mainam%2C%20an%20MMA%20fighter%20from%20Manipur%20and%20an%20acquaintance%20from%20his%20first%20stint%20in%20wrestling.%20Following%20the%20National%20Games%20debacle%2C%20Chungreng%20told%20Roshan%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20train%20and%20compete%20in%20MMA%20because%20there%20was%20nothing%20else%20left%20for%20him.%20At%20this%20time%2C%20Roshan%20was%20trying%20out%20for%20Evolve%20MMA%2C%20a%20renowned%20Singapore-based%20gym%2C%20which%20produces%20fighters%20for%20ONE%20Championship%20%E2%80%94%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20most%20recognised%20MMA%20promotion%20%E2%80%94%20and%20other%20major%20promotions%20from%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Roshan%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20met%20sometime%20in%202006%20at%20junior%20wrestling%20tournaments%20in%20Manipur%20although%20he%20was%20competing%20in%20a%20higher%20weight%20category.%20By%202018%2C%20as%20I%20was%20getting%20recognised%20for%20MMA%20in%20the%20Northeast%2C%20he%20saw%20the%20potential%20of%20making%20the%20switch%20from%20wrestling.%20After%20seeing%20the%20recognition%20I%20was%20getting%2C%20we%20got%20in%20touch.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFollowing%20some%20success%20in%20the%20sport%2C%20my%20financial%20situation%20started%20to%20get%20better.%20In%20November%202018%2C%20I%20was%20selected%20to%20train%20at%20the%20prestigious%20Evolve%20MMA%20gym%20in%20Singapore.%20But%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20earlier%2C%20while%20I%20was%20training%20at%20Koi%20Combat%20Academy%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20I%20invited%20Chungreng%20to%20come%20down%20and%20train%20there.%20Initially%2C%20I%20took%20care%20of%20all%20his%20expenses%20to%20train%20at%20the%20academy%20because%20he%20was%20not%20in%20a%20good%20place%20financially%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRoshan%20invited%20me%20to%20train%20at%20Koi%20Combat%20Academy%20and%20trained%20me%20for%20about%20two%20months%20before%20leaving%20for%20Singapore%2C%20following%20which%20Vishal%20%5BSeigell%5D%20Sir%20took%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Chungreng.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20selection%20to%20Evolve%20MMA%2C%20Roshan%20signed%20a%20%2448%2C000-a-year%20contract%20for%20three%20years%20in%20which%20he%20would%20train%20full-time%20and%20compete%20in%20ONE%20Championship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20I%20was%20training%20in%20Singapore%2C%20I%20was%20helping%20fighters%20like%20Chungreng%20who%20were%20struggling%20financially.%20The%20reason%20why%20I%20support%20fighters%20like%20him%20is%20because%20I%20come%20from%20similar%20circumstances.%20I%20grew%20up%20as%20a%20sickly%20child%20in%20a%20poor%20family%20with%20a%20chronically%20sick%20father%20and%20a%20mother%20who%20worked%20extremely%20hard%20at%20a%20rice%20mill%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Roshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20money%20to%20train%20when%20I%20first%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20to%20train%20in%20MMA%2C%20and%20thankfully%20had%20coaches%20there%20who%20supported%20me%20similarly.%20So%2C%20I%20promised%20to%20myself%20that%20if%20I%20ever%20earned%20any%20notoriety%20in%20the%20sport%2C%20I%20would%20help%20other%20fighters%20after%20me%20from%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20whatever%20support%20Roshan%20could%20offer%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20and%20Chungreng%20was%20still%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20When%20COVID-19%20struck%2C%20Chungreng%20left%20Bengaluru%20and%20his%20MMA%20dreams%20were%20hanging%20in%20th