2_blank%5C%22%3Eretellings%20of%20the%20history%20and%20heritage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Kochi.%20Within%20their%20pages%2C%20they%20hold%20fascinating%20accounts%20of%20how%20the%20city%20evolved%20into%20its%20present%20form%2C%20backed%20by%20intriguing%20anecdotes.%20The%20content%20would%20leave%20any%20history%20buff%20spellbound.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20delivery%20agent%20rings%20the%20doorbell%2C%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20wait%20long.%20A%20man%20in%20his%20thirties%20opens%20the%20door%20within%20seconds.%20It%E2%80%99s%20almost%20as%20if%20he%20were%20waiting%20impatiently%20for%20this%20moment!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnthusiasm%20is%20etched%20on%20Johann%20Kuruvilla%E2%80%99s%20face%20as%20he%20tears%20open%20the%20package%2C%20hungrily%20eyeing%20his%20next%20reads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20books%20find%20their%20way%20to%20a%20home%20library%20which%20already%20boasts%20over%20300%20books.%20%E2%80%9COne%20can%20never%20have%20enough%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330111%2Ftanya-abraham-journalist-writes-eating-with-history-kerala-food-recipes-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebooks%20around%20heritage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Johann.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20who%20would%20like%20to%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20in%20those%20books%20%E2%80%94%20the%20secrets%20of%20South%20India%20and%20first-hand%20stories%20of%20the%20lores%20surrounding%20Fort%20Kochi%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20two%20ways.%20Either%20you%20ask%20Johann%20to%20share%20his%20reading%20list%20or%20you%20attend%20one%20of%20the%20many%20experiential%20walks%20organised%20by%20him%20and%20his%20team%20as%20part%20of%20%E2%80%98Kochi%20Heritage%20Project%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Not%20shy%20of%20my%20heritage.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3C